annotations.title: 10 Easy Cocktails To Make At Home

textContent:
.5oz simple syrup
4 rasberries
.75oz lime
2oz gin

Muddle then whip shake with crushed ice.
Pour into glass then top with crushed ice. 
Garnish with lime and rasberry.
